[SPEAKER_01]: Meet in community spaces, city halls, parks, libraries, coffee shops.

1126
02:58:25,020 --> 02:58:26,201
[SPEAKER_01]: The potential is limitless.

1127
02:58:27,462 --> 02:58:29,563
[SPEAKER_01]: And have meaningful conversations.

1128
02:58:30,384 --> 02:58:31,625
[SPEAKER_01]: Get to know one another.

1129
02:58:33,066 --> 02:58:38,470
[SPEAKER_01]: Speak respectfully and honestly, even when it feels uncomfortable.

1130
02:58:40,522 --> 02:58:45,127
[SPEAKER_01]: for what is growth without a little discomfort.

1131
02:58:47,289 --> 02:58:49,712
[SPEAKER_01]: Connection starts with showing up first.

1132
02:58:51,470 --> 02:58:56,193
[SPEAKER_01]: Second, let your faith be a force for unity.

1133
02:58:57,454 --> 02:59:11,502
[SPEAKER_01]: Whether you find it in a mosque, a temple, a church, or a quiet moment in nature, let your faith inspire you to reach out, learn, and build bridges.

1134
02:59:12,863 --> 02:59:20,788
[SPEAKER_01]: As Celia reminded me in her speech with us today, one of our shared prophets said,

1135
02:59:22,351 --> 02:59:24,092
[SPEAKER_01]: Faith, hope, and love.

1136
02:59:25,432 --> 02:59:27,433
[SPEAKER_01]: Let these be held amongst you.

1137
02:59:28,734 --> 02:59:30,955
[SPEAKER_01]: But the greatest of these is love.

1138
02:59:33,556 --> 02:59:49,082
[SPEAKER_01]: And for my own faith tradition, which I believe amplifies that message, none of you have faith until you love for your brother what you love for yourself.

1139
02:59:52,275 --> 02:59:58,397
[SPEAKER_01]: Now finally, be a voice for what is fair, just, and true.

1140
03:00:00,918 --> 03:00:05,900
[SPEAKER_01]: Vote not just as a civic duty, but as an expression of hope and accountability.

1141
03:00:06,940 --> 03:00:08,621
[SPEAKER_01]: Advocate for what is right.

1142
03:00:09,261 --> 03:00:18,444
[SPEAKER_01]: Encourage others to stay hopeful, engaged, and grounded in love, even when the world provokes us to anger or despair.

1143
03:00:20,307 --> 03:00:28,932
[SPEAKER_01]: and remember to do it without compromise to yourself and with the best of intentions and integrity.

1144
03:00:30,933 --> 03:00:40,878
[SPEAKER_01]: Dr. King dreamed of an America where people are judged by the content of their character, not by the color of their skin.

1145
03:00:43,024 --> 03:00:51,470
[SPEAKER_01]: And I dare say that he would even add to that now as we seek to divide ourselves even more with arbitrary labels.

1146
03:00:54,232 --> 03:01:03,198
[SPEAKER_01]: He envisioned a nation where darkness is driven out by light and where love transforms enemies into friends.

1147
03:01:04,379 --> 03:01:07,361
[SPEAKER_01]: That dream belongs to all of us.

1148
03:01:08,842 --> 03:01:11,144
[SPEAKER_01]: We each hold a piece of it.

1149
03:01:12,181 --> 03:01:18,622
[SPEAKER_01]: And when we come together, those pieces form something extraordinary.

1150
03:01:20,433 --> 03:01:37,357
[SPEAKER_01]: So as we leave here today, let us carry forward the sacred trust of Reverend Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr., his vision, his courage, and his unyielding faith in the power of community.

1151
03:01:38,477 --> 03:01:42,638
[SPEAKER_01]: Dr. King once said, not everybody can be famous.

1152
03:01:43,658 --> 03:01:50,582
[SPEAKER_01]: But everybody can be great because greatness is determined by service.

1153
03:01:52,163 --> 03:01:58,968
[SPEAKER_01]: So I invite you all today, when you leave here, join together in that service.

1154
03:02:00,929 --> 03:02:02,850
[SPEAKER_01]: Thank you for being here today.

1155
03:02:03,491 --> 03:02:11,936
[SPEAKER_01]: Thank you for your determination to serve and for your commitment to living out the promise of Dr. King's dream.

1156
03:02:13,376 --> 03:02:31,744
[SPEAKER_01]: not just his dream, but I believe the dream of everyone who has struggled and fought so that we may all be equal to each other, so that we may all love one another as human beings.

1157
03:02:32,584 --> 03:02:32,884
[SPEAKER_01]: Thank you.

1158
03:02:42,947 --> 03:02:46,471
[SPEAKER_07]: All right okay.

1159
03:02:47,712 --> 03:02:58,844
